column2: SELECT p.objid, p.ra, p.dec, p.petror9#_r, s.z as z_spec, s.zErr,     zns.nvote, zns.p_el as elliptical, zns.p_cw as spiralclock, zns.p_acw as spiralanticlock,     zns.p_edge as edgeon, zns.p_dk as dontknow, zns.p_mg as merger   FROM Galaxy as p    JOIN ZooNoSpec AS zns ON p.objid = zns.objid    JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE p.clean=# and zns.nvote >= # and zns.p_el > # and p.petror9#_r>#   and p.ra between # and #   and s.z between # and #
